      • toJsonObject

        public javax.json.JsonObject toJsonObject()
        For each line of squares it builds a JsonArray that will be added to a JsonArray containing every line of the board. Building it in this way makes it possible to scan it with a JsonArray used to build the strings of the cli. This method creates a JsonObject containing all the information needed in the View. The said JsonObject will add up to every other JsonObject of every other (necessary) class and will be sent to the view when needed.
        Returns:
        The JsonObject of the board.
